narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: The library's one day check out policy was difficult
The budget for the full scale prototype was low and prohibited some of the projects from being developed further. I would recommend a higher budget through the school or an outside organization.
Resources were fine. The $200 allowance was used and needs to remain in place.
